{"tid":2452890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英女皇聞悉哈里指控「感傷心但不憤怒」 威廉苦惱兄弟對話外洩","createTime":"2021-03-19T06:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T08:55:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c18ae4af44cca7d75b6cf62598ee4ee467b9a995","tid":2452890,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"英國哈里王子及妻子梅根在接受美國名嘴奧花雲費的專訪中，公開指控皇室存在種族歧視。有消息人士透露，英女皇聞訊後「感到傷心卻不憤怒」，但哈里哥哥威廉王子則對兄弟間的對話外洩感到苦惱，擔心會被美國傳媒越描越黑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/RPHBJCOUMBHJDKEQGD6OKOO67Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FRPHBJCOUMBHJDKEQGD6OKOO67Y%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=faa4df29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FRPHBJCOUMBHJDKEQGD6OKOO67Y%2F&h=eddbf748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/RPHBJCOUMBHJDKEQGD6OKOO67Y/</a>"},{"pid":"818fdfda8883c1c0fa90018b0a19c86a24ee9488","tid":2452890,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"兩兄弟傾計 即係細佬爆料啦"},{"pid":"92bae37ecd51a88d26421c02536cc859ab347f72","tid":2452890,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"818fdfda8883c1c0fa90018b0a19c86a24ee9488","tid":2452890,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"兩兄弟傾計 即係細佬爆料啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">哈里不一樣。哈里沒有接受命運，他要抗爭。戴妃已屍骨不存，但他和王室競爭媽媽的戰爭還沒結束。也許他還會想，媽媽為自己展示過自由之夢的一瞬間，如果自己獨立不成功，就對不起媽媽。現在他只有同樣不滿意的梅根作自己的同伴，還有在大西洋另一邊的左翼和自由派為自己搖旗吶喊。他也許不知道，同樣是對現狀不滿，自己的理由比妻子的充份得多，愛恨交纏也理應有更多層次。然最後一定是梅根贏，因為她賭本是別人的，哈里卻是自己睹自己。即使他最後毀了王室，他也一無所有。戰爭開始的時候，他就已經輸了。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">MAR 14, 2021 AT 5:51 PM<br />\n小王子的伊底帕斯情結</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/48731355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F48731355&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=265bf390\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/48731355</a>"},{"pid":"9d725e1b654fd282575bc7c8924c8bcd43f65367","tid":2452890,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"話曬都係一家人,又經歷過咁多風浪,呢D喺佢眼中其實只係小事黎,唔通嬲左個孫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}